{
  "stem": "20581.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And by the way, also in Lemberg, this cousin of mine-- actually, I could say he was the first one who, actually, was one of the first ones, who started the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Which [NON-ENGLISH] means so-- flight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So being he was in charge, he was a big deal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So like in Russia, to go from one place to another, you need a-- it's not called a [NON-ENGLISH], but it's called a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Like a ID-- you cannot go from one place to another without having any kind of documents papers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he is the one who used to sign all these papers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was started out in [NON-ENGLISH] with a few of the Jewish people who were signers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said that we have to start to try to go to get to Israel.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there, one time, some people tried to smuggle the border between Poland and Romania.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they got caught.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Two or three of them got killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they found the ID which my cousin signed, that he's the one who gave them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that time, I was in Lemberg, and we lived in Lvov also.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I told him that they were looking for him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I came down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I told him that we have to run from this [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we got together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we ran.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so where did we go?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went to Przemysl.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Przemysl is a big city in Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you was asking before if I wore a Russian uniform.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then what happened on that time, he's the one who made papers for me and for himself that we are Russian intelligence, like [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was having-- I was wearing a Russian uniform.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was wearing a Russian uniform.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we can came to Przemysl.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
